last_episode_to_air.name: The Last Adventure!
last_episode_to_air.overview: The future of adventuring hangs in the balance as the Duck family uncovers earth-shattering secrets in a final standoff with F.O.W.L.

name: DuckTales
overview: The adventures of billionaire Scrooge McDuck and his nephews Huey, Dewey and Louie, their famous uncle Donald Duck, pilot extraordinaire Launchpad, Mrs. Beakly, Webby and Roboduck. Adventures and hidden treasures are everywhere, in their hometown Duckburg and all around the world.

episodes.name: Woo-oo!
episodes.overview: Donald Duck reluctantly takes his nephews Huey, Dewey and Louie to the home of their reclusive great-uncle Scrooge McDuck. Enthralled by their once legendary great-uncle and the wonder of McDuck Manor, the triplets and their newfound fierce friend Webby learn of long-kept family secrets and unleash totems from Scrooge's epic past, sending the family on an adventure of a lifetime to the Lost City of Atlantis.

episodes.name: Daytrip of Doom!
episodes.overview: The nephews take Webby to Funso's Fun Zone and have a dangerous run-in with the Beagle Boys.

guest_stars.character: Big Time Beagle / Bouncer Beagle / Burger Beagle (voice)
guest_stars.name: Eric Bauza

episodes.name: The Great Dime Chase!
episodes.overview: Louie accidentally spends Scrooge's Number One Dime and turns to mad inventor Gyro Gearloose for help to get it back, while Dewey and Webby become entangled in a conspiracy.

guest_stars.character: Mrs. Quackfaster / Secretary / Lock Pick Lady (voice)
guest_stars.name: Susanne Blakeslee

episodes.name: The Beagle Birthday Massacre!
episodes.overview: After crashing Ma Beagle's birthday party, Webby and new mysterious friend Lena must fight their way through Beagle Boy turf to get back home.

episodes.name: Terror of the Terra-Firmians!
episodes.overview: Huey and Webby's disagreement over the existence of a mythic species leads the kids to explore an eerie abandoned subway tunnel, while Mrs. Beakley grows suspicious of Lena.

episodes.name: The House of the Lucky Gander!
episodes.overview: Donald competes with his cousin Gladstone Gander to impress Louie at a mysterious resort in Macaw, while Scrooge tries to lure the kids away from the resort’s endless distractions.

episodes.name: The Infernal Internship of Mark Beaks!
episodes.overview: Huey competes with Dewey for a coveted internship with Duckburg's newest tech billionaire, Mark Beaks, while Scrooge and Glomgold team up to take this new competitor down.

episodes.name: The Living Mummies of Toth-Ra!
episodes.overview: In a lost pyramid, Louie interprets a pharaoh's prophecy to his advantage, forcing Scrooge and Launchpad to convince a group of living mummies to rescue him.

episodes.name: The Impossible Summit of Mt. Neverrest
episodes.overview: Scrooge and Huey are determined to be the first to set foot atop an impossible summit, but the snow-capped mountain holds a treacherous secret that tests both their commitment and survival.

episodes.name: The Spear of Selene!
episodes.overview: Donald is dragged into a feud between Scrooge and Zeus, while Dewey and Webby search for an artifact that may provide the truth about Dewey’s mother.

episodes.name: Beware the B.U.D.D.Y. System!
episodes.overview: Brilliant young scientist Fenton Crackshell-Cabrera is recruited by Launchpad who is feeling menaced by tech genius Mark Beaks’ newest invention.

episodes.name: The Missing Links of Moorshire!
episodes.overview: Dewey’s natural golf abilities challenge Scrooge’s ego while, a seemingly innocent, mystical golf course leads the group into trouble.

episodes.name: McMystery at McDuck McManor!
episodes.overview: When Scrooge unexpectedly disappears during his birthday party, Huey, Dewey and Louie find themselves hosting a mystery party where everyone is a suspect.

episodes.name: JAW$!
episodes.overview: The kids and Launchpad work together to capture a mystical money shark while Scrooge attempts to better his public image with a televised interview.

episodes.name: The Golden Lagoon of White Agony Plains!
episodes.overview: Scrooge reteams with his conniving ex-partner and old flame, Goldie O’ Gilt, to find a long-lost golden lagoon, but Glomgold has other plans.

guest_stars.character: Flintheart Glomgold / General Store Owner / Duck Waiter (voice)
guest_stars.name: Keith Ferguson

episodes.name: Day of the Only Child!
episodes.overview: When Dewey invents a holiday that allows the triplets to be only children for a day, each realizes they need their brothers more than they thought.

guest_stars.character: Bouncer Beagle / Big Time Beagle / Burger Beagle (voice)
guest_stars.name: Eric Bauza

episodes.name: From the Confidential Casefiles of Agent 22!
episodes.overview: Webby learns how Scrooge and Mrs. Beakley first met while she helps Scrooge rescue her granny from the clutches of rival spy Black Heron.

episodes.name: Who is Gizmoduck?!
episodes.overview: As Fenton figures out how to be a hero, Mark Beaks offers to hire Gizmoduck and help him defend all of Duckburg.

guest_stars.character: Big Time Beagle / Bouncer Beagle / Burger Beagle (voice)
guest_stars.name: Eric Bauza

episodes.name: The Other Bin of Scrooge McDuck!
episodes.overview: Lena’s loyalties are tested when Magica forces her to lead Webby on a raid to a facility full of Scrooge’s most dangerous artifacts to find his #1 Dime.

episodes.name: Sky Pirates...In the Sky!
episodes.overview: Feeling ignored, Dewey finds a new family: a band of singing and dancing pirates looking to rob Scrooge blind.

guest_stars.character: Peg Leg Meg / Hardtack Hattie / One-Eyed Linda (voice)
guest_stars.name: Kimberly Brooks

episodes.name: The Secret(s) of Castle McDuck!
episodes.overview: On a family trip to Scrooge’s ancestral castle, Dewey tries to hide the truth about his mom as his brothers search for family secrets.

episodes.name: The Last Crash of the Sunchaser!
episodes.overview: Stuck on a precarious peak, the kids secretly search the plane for the final clue about Della’s mysterious disappearance.

episodes.name: The Shadow War
episodes.overview: Magica De Spell is close to exacting revenge on Scrooge, so the family races against time to plan a dangerous rescue mission to save Scrooge and the city.

episodes.name: The Most Dangerous Game...Night!
episodes.overview: A game night is anything but relaxing as the family faces shrink rays, a barbaric civilization and an unhealthy level of competitiveness.

episodes.name: The Depths of Cousin Fethry!
episodes.overview: Huey and Dewey are led on an adventure by their distant Uncle Fethry, who takes them to the depths of Scrooge’s deep‐sea laboratory.

episodes.name: The Ballad of Duke Baloney!
episodes.overview: After his disappearance, Glomgold resurfaces as anything but his ever-scheming self, while Webby and Louie try to uncover the truth behind who is Duke Baloney.

episodes.name: The Town Where Everyone Was Nice!
episodes.overview: The family visits a Brazilian town with a dark secret where Donald reunites with his old friends Jose Carioca & Panchito Pistoles, thus reuniting The Three Caballeros.

episodes.name: Storkules in Duckburg!
episodes.overview: Louie recruits Storkules for his professional monster extermination business, while Storkules faces his greatest challenge: being Donald’s roommate.

guest_stars.character: Big Time Beagle / Funso Doll / Funso (voice)
guest_stars.name: Eric Bauza

episodes.name: Last Christmas!
episodes.overview: Scrooge avoids the pressures of the holidays by traveling back in time with a trio of fun-loving ghosts to crash history's greatest Christmas parties; time-lost Dewey teams up with young Donald Duck to find his mother on Christmas.

episodes.name: What Ever Happened to Della Duck?!
episodes.overview: Della struggles for survival against dangerous elements of the Moon, as she looks for a way to get back to her family on Earth.

episodes.name: Treasure of the Found Lamp!
episodes.overview: As the boys track a missing artifact across Duckburg, Scrooge and Webby stall the warrior looking for it with a phony quest.

episodes.name: The Outlaw Scrooge McDuck!
episodes.overview: In the Old West, Scrooge and Goldie form a band of outlaws and stage a heist to save a small town from corrupt businessman John D. Rockerduck.

episodes.name: The 87 Cent Solution!
episodes.overview: The kids must stop Scrooge’s unhealthy obsession with a few missing coins to keep him from becoming the next Glomgold.

episodes.name: The Golden Spear!
episodes.overview: As Della rebuilds her ship, Penumbra becomes convinced Della’s planning an attack. Meanwhile, Donald’s nap keeps getting interrupted by adventure.

episodes.name: Nothing Can Stop Della Duck!
episodes.overview: Della Duck has faced every danger the moon has to offer to reunite with her family, but her greatest challenge is one she might not be able to fight her way out of.

episodes.name: Raiders of the Doomsday Vault!
episodes.overview: Dewey tries to prove himself by exploring a frozen fortress in search of a money tree seed, but Glomgold has kidnapped Scrooge in order to find it first.

guest_stars.character: Ludwig Von Drake / Corvus Von Drake (voice)
guest_stars.name: Corey Burton

guest_stars.character: Anya Von Drake / Klara Von Drake (voice)
guest_stars.name: Kari Wahlgren

episodes.name: Friendship Hates Magic!
episodes.overview: Stuck as a shadow, Lena tries to protect Webby from her suspicious new friend Violet during a supernatural Sleepover.

episodes.name: The Dangerous Chemistry of Gandra Dee!
episodes.overview: With Huey’s and Webby’s help, Fenton woos a punk-rock scientist, Gandra Dee, only to uncover her dangerous plans for Gizmoduck.

episodes.name: The Duck Knight Returns!
episodes.overview: After he and Dewey meet Darkwing Duck's original actor Jim Starling and then find out that Scrooge intend to make a gritty movie about Darkwing Duck with a new actor, both Launchpad and Jim are against it.

episodes.name: What Ever Happened to Donald Duck?!
episodes.overview: Donald and Penumbra must break out of a Moon Prison and send a warning to Earth about a looming invasion. Meanwhile, Dewey and Webby uncover a sinister conspiracy targeting their family.

episodes.name: Happy Birthday, Doofus Drake!
episodes.overview: Louie teams with Goldie to scam their way through Doofus' dangerous party. Huey pushes himself out of his comfort zone in his favorite online game.

episodes.name: A Nightmare on Killmotor Hill!
episodes.overview: The kids are pulled into a world made of their wildest dreams. Unfortunately, Lena’s worst nightmare comes true: Magica De Spell is back and coming to reclaim what’s hers.

episodes.name: The Golden Armory of Cornelius Coot!
episodes.overview: Webby leads the kids in a race against the Beagles to find a secret treasure while hiding a secret of her own. Della is forced to teach Launchpad how to actually fly a plane.

episodes.name: Timephoon!
episodes.overview: When Louie uses Gyro’s Time Tub to steal lost treasures from the past, a mysterious storm in the present sends all of space and time crashing down onto the mansion.

episodes.name: GlomTales!
episodes.overview: Glomgold forms his own family made of all of Scrooge’s greatest villains to defeat Scrooge’s family once and for all.

episodes.name: The Richest Duck in the World!
episodes.overview: Louie, Scrooge and Owlson must escape from an unstoppable monster cursed to hunt down and destroy the richest duck in the world.

episodes.name: Moonvasion!
episodes.overview: The moon invades Duckburg, forcing Scrooge to join forces with an unlikely ally in an effort to save the earth. Meanwhile, Della and the kids search the globe for reinforcements.

episodes.name: Challenge of the Senior Junior Woodchucks!
episodes.overview: Huey races against Violet in a challenge to be named Senior Junior Woodchuck, while Scrooge and the family search for a secret Woodchuck treasure.

episodes.name: Quack Pack!
episodes.overview: The family is not quite themselves as they discover the planned family photoshoot might just be a part of a bigger “wish” gone wrong.

episodes.name: Double-O-Duck in You Only Crash Twice!
episodes.overview: A spy video game turns dangerously real as Launchpad and Dewey must stop F.O.W.L. agent Steelbeak’s plan to destroy Duckburg.

guest_stars.character: Prospector Paul / Ticket Stand Clerk / Dealer (voice)
guest_stars.name: Eric Bauza

episodes.name: The Lost Harp of Mervana!
episodes.overview: The family joins a zen mermaid society to find a missing mystery, but Louie is convinced the seemingly innocent mermaids have a villainous agenda of their own.

episodes.name: Louie's Eleven!
episodes.overview: Louie plans a break-in at a high-class party hosted by Duckburg’s most popular tastemaker, Emma Glamour, so the Three Caballeros can play as Donald tries to get past the party’s no-nonsense planner, Daisy Duck.

episodes.name: Astro B.O.Y.D.!
episodes.overview: Gyro, Fenton and Huey take a malfunctioning B.O.Y.D. back to the lab where he was created in Japan, but as Huey bonds with the robot boy, a secret from Gyro’s past threatens to destroy the city and Gizmoduck.

episodes.name: The Rumble for Ragnarok!
episodes.overview: Dewey must embrace his inner heel to beat beloved Viking wrestling champ Jormungandr in a battle royale for the fate of the Earth.

episodes.name: The Phantom and the Sorceress
episodes.overview: When a mysterious magic thief arrives in Duckburg, Lena must confront her past and team with her treacherous aunt, Magica.

episodes.name: They Put a Moonlander on the Earth!
episodes.overview: Webby sets out to prove to a homesick Penumbra that Earth can be a lot of fun by riding Glomgold’s newest gift to Duckburg, the suspicious Flintferris Glomwheel.

episodes.name: The Trickening!
episodes.overview: The kids forego their usual trick-or-treat path and instead take on the most haunted house in Duckburg, while Launchpad confronts ghosts from the past.

episodes.name: The Forbidden Fountain of the Foreverglades!
episodes.overview: Scrooge and Goldie O’Gilt are turned into teenagers as they race Rockerduck to the Fountain of Youth, while the boys’ sibling rivalry uncovers danger at a spring break hotel.

episodes.name: Let's Get Dangerous!
episodes.overview: Darkwing gains an unlikely sidekick as he uncovers a dark conspiracy tied to the Missing Mysteries and one of Scrooge’s employees.

episodes.name: Escape from the ImpossiBin!
episodes.overview: With F.O.W.L. at their heels, Scrooge tests out the Money Bin’s new security system on Louie and Della, while Beakley and Webby train the others for an enemy attack.

episodes.name: The Split Sword of Swanstantine!
episodes.overview: The kids pair off to find the missing pieces of a mystical sword hidden throughout a marketplace, unless F.O.W.L. gets to them first.

episodes.name: New Gods on the Block!
episodes.overview: The kids try to prove themselves by auditioning to take Zeus' place amongst the Greek gods, while Storkules interferes with Donald and Daisy's date.

episodes.name: The First Adventure!
episodes.overview: Scrooge is forced to babysit young Donald and Della as they go on their first adventure to find a powerful artifact, unaware that Bradford is taking on this mission personally.

episodes.name: The Fight for Castle McDuck!
episodes.overview: A bitter feud between Scrooge and his sister, Matilda, spreads to the rest of the family as Phantom Blot attempts to steal a priceless artifact and destroy Castle McDuck once and for all.

guest_stars.name: Ashley Jensen

episodes.name: How Santa Stole Christmas!
episodes.overview: Scrooge teams up with his archrival, Santa Claus, to save Christmas, while Webby discovers the true history behind their infamous feud.

guest_stars.character: Bouncer Beagle / Big Time Beagle / Beagle Boys (voice)
guest_stars.name: Eric Bauza

episodes.name: Beaks in the Shell!
episodes.overview: Huey struggles to keep Fenton and Gandra’s top-secret experiment (and their relationship) hidden from the world. But, Mark Beaks is desperate for one last gizmo to steal.

episodes.name: The Lost Cargo of Kit Cloudkicker!
episodes.overview: Della, Dewey and Huey recruit a showboating pilot to take them to an island full of monsters in search of a missing mystery, unaware that Don Karnage is hot on their tails.

guest_stars.character: Peg Leg Meg / Hard Tack Hattie (voice)
guest_stars.name: Kimberly Brooks

episodes.name: The Life And Crimes of Scrooge McDuck!
episodes.overview: Scrooge's enemies reveal a secret history to prove that he is responsible for turning them evil, forcing Louie to defend his uncle against their prosecutor, Doofus Drake.

guest_stars.name: Kari Wahlgren
